      <h3>Daily Usage</h3>
      <p>Ongoing activity centers on driving traffic to the Mega Link — through social media posts, content, or paid ads — and attending or rewatching live training sessions.</p>
      <h3>Learning Curve</h3>
      <p>Sources consistently describe the system as low-friction for people with no technical background, since OLSP supplies the funnel and follow-up sequences. The trade-off is less customization and more dependence on OLSP's own sales process.</p>
      <h3>Interface &amp; Usability</h3>
      <p>We could not verify interface usability first-hand. Several independent reviewers describe the dashboard as straightforward, but none of these are neutral, fully independent sources — most are themselves promoting their own referral link.</p>
