      <p><strong>Unique selling point:</strong> OLSP's main differentiator is the single "Mega Link" concept, which removes the need to build a website or funnel from scratch. <strong>Trade-off:</strong> that simplicity comes from funneling new members into OLSP's own paid tiers, rather than from selling outside products directly.</p>
